verbose_text: To test this hypothesis, naive F5 CD8 + T cells expressing either physiological levels of wild-type L-selectin (F5/B6) or increased levels of L-selectin (F5/LDeltaP) (XREF_FIG A and 2B; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY) were transferred into B6 mice, the mice were challenged the following day with vaccNP and ovaries, and ovdLNs and spleens were analyzed for donor cells (XREF_FIG C).
